{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"ida97fed28-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2473"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2473"},"text":"§ 2473.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Annual five-year plans on improvement of depot infrastructure","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"ida97fed29-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2473/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Submission","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"As part of the annual budget submission of the President under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t31/s1105/a"},"text":"section 1105(a) of title 31","children":[],"tail":", each Secretary of a military department shall submit to the congressional defense committees a plan describing the objectives of that Secretary to improve depot infrastructure during the five fiscal years following the fiscal year for which such budget is submitted."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"ida97fed2a-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2473/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Elements","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"Each plan submitted by a Secretary of a military department under subsection (a) shall include the following:","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida97fed2b-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2473/b/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" With respect to the five-year period covered by the plan, an identification of the major lines of effort, milestones, and specific goals of the Secretary over such period relating to the improvement of depot infrastructure and a description of how such goals support the goals outlined in section 359(b)(1)(B) of the National Defense Authorization Act for Fiscal Year 2020 (","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/92"},"text":"Public Law 116–92","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/133/1324"},"text":"133 Stat. 1324","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s2476"},"text":"10 U.S.C. 2476","children":[],"tail":" note)."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida97fed2c-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2473/b/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The estimated costs of necessary depot infrastructure improvements and a description of how such costs would be addressed by the Department of Defense budget request submitted during the same year as the plan and the applicable future-years defense program.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida97fed2d-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2473/b/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Information regarding the plan of the Secretary to initiate such environmental and engineering studies as may be necessary to carry out planned depot infrastructure improvements.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida97fed2e-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2473/b/4"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4"},"text":"(4)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Detailed information regarding how depot infrastructure improvement projects will be paced and sequenced to ensure continuous operations.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"ida97fed2f-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2473/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Incorporation of Results-oriented Management Practices","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"Each plan under subsection (a) shall incorporate the leading results-oriented management practices identified in the report of the Comptroller General of the United States titled “Actions Needed to Improve Poor Conditions of Facilities and Equipment that Affect Maintenance Timeliness and Efficiency” (GAO–19–242), or any successor report, including—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida97fed30-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2473/c/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" analytically based goals;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida97fed31-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2473/c/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" results-oriented metrics;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida97fed32-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2473/c/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the identification of required resources, risks, and stakeholders; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida97fed33-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2473/c/4"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4"},"text":"(4)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" regular reporting on progress to decision makers.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"ida97fed34-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"(Added ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/263/dA/tIII/s373"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–263, div. A, title III, § 373","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2022-12-23"},"text":"Dec. 23, 2022","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/136/2540"},"text":"136 Stat. 2540","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"ida97fed35-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"ida97fed36-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"ida97fed37-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/263/s373"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–263, § 373","children":[],"tail":", which directed amendment of this chapter by adding this section after section “2742”, was executed by adding this section after section 2472 to reflect the probable intent of Congress."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"priorProvisions","id":"ida97fed38-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Prior Provisions","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"A prior section 2473, added ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/201/dA/tVIII/s832/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–201, div. A, title VIII, § 832(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1996-09-23"},"text":"Sept. 23, 1996","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/110/2616"},"text":"110 Stat. 2616","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/261/dA/tVIII/s809/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–261, div. A, title VIII, § 809(a)","children":[],"tail":"–(d), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1998-10-17"},"text":"Oct. 17, 1998","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/112/2085"},"text":"112 Stat. 2085","children":[],"tail":", 2086; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/106/65/dA/tVIII/s815/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 106–65, div. A, title VIII, § 815(b)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1999-10-05"},"text":"Oct. 5, 1999","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/113/712"},"text":"113 Stat. 712","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/84/dA/tVIII/s818/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–84, div. A, title VIII, § 818(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2009-10-28"},"text":"Oct. 28, 2009","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/123/2408"},"text":"123 Stat. 2408","children":[],"tail":", required the Secretary of Defense to place conditions on the procurement of property or services in order to preserve the small arms production industrial base, prior to repeal by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/383/dA/tVIII/s822/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–383, div. A, title VIII, § 822(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2011-01-07"},"text":"Jan. 7, 2011","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/124/4268"},"text":"124 Stat. 4268","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
